name: ULTRA-ILLUSI0N 2D
description:
ULTRA-ILLUSI0N 2D

2.5D Model Here

This model was originally created as a personal exercise for me to practice creating merged models, but it turned out better than I expected, so I'm sharing it. All three elements - background, figure, and human body - are generated with a style and quality that I personally find quite pleasing.

modelVersions.name: ULTRA-ILLUSI0N 2D V1
modelVersions.description:
V1 1.1 Changelogs :

  • Re-uploaded as a 2D model (the 2.5D model will be uploaded at a later date as ULTRA-ILLUSI0N 2.5D)

  • The merge expression looks like this:
    WSB x 0.5 + camelliamix_v20 x 0.5 = UI1
    UI1 + (camelliamix_v20 - dualPersonality_dualblack) x 0.5 = UI2(ULTRA-ILLUSI0N 2.5D V1)
    UI2 x 0.25 + MIX-Pro-V3.5 x 0.5 + kawaii2D_kawaii2DPrunedFp16 x 0.25 = UIA(ULTRA-ILLUSI0N 2D V1)
